## âœ… **What is Linux?**

Linux is an **open-source operating system** like Windows or macOS.
It manages hardware and runs applications on computers and servers.

---

## âœ… **Why Do We Use Linux? (Short & Simple)**

* Free & Open Source â†’ No license cost
* Very Secure â†’ Harder to hack
* Fast & Stable â†’ Rarely crashes
* Best for Servers â†’ 90% cloud & DevOps tools run on Linux
* Customizable â†’ You can modify anything
* Lightweight â†’ Runs on low hardware

